{"tid":1370622,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"民建聯緊急呼籲：區外市民盡量勿到元朗","createTime":"2019-07-27T05:00:48.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-27T12:55:31.000Z","uid":212626,"like":2,"dislike":583,"uniUserReply":85,"replies":[{"pid":"c66e33f714dbd5b25b1401623f906abf657ae217","tid":1370622,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T05:00:48.000Z","msg":"公眾集會及遊行上訴委員會昨日駁回 7.27「光復元朗」遊行申請人鍾健平的上訴，維持禁止遊行，外界預料不少市民仍然會前往元朗。立法會第一大黨、建制派民建聯今日下午 12 時許發出緊急呼籲，籲為保障自身安全及避免個人出現法律風險，區外的市民盡量不要前往元朗，並呼籲各方保持克制，不要作出挑釁的行為。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">民建聯今日發緊急呼籲，指昨日公眾集會及遊行上訴委員會駁回有關今天在元朗舉行遊行申請的上訴，這表示有關的遊行會被視為不合法，參與者有可能面對法律風險。</span><br />\n<br />\n民建聯指出，根據各方面的消息，相信亦有為數不少的市民會以各種方式前往元朗表達意見，社會高度關注今日元朗可能出現的各種情況，而區內的街坊對可能出現的衝突混亂場面表示非常憂慮。<br />\n<br />\n民建聯呼籲，為保障自身安全及避免個人出現法律風險，區外的市民盡量不要前往元朗；若認為需要前往表達意見的人士，也應維持和平理性的方式，「我們也呼籲各方保持克制，不要作出挑釁的行為；同時，我們要求警方作好部署，盡最大的努力維持秩序，必要時採取果斷的執法行動，以維護法治，保障市民的安全。」<br />\n<a href=\"https://thestandnews.com/politics/%E6%B0%91%E5%BB%BA%E8%81%AF%E7%B7%8A%E6%80%A5%E5%91%BC%E7%B1%B2-%E5%8D%80%E5%A4%96%E5%B8%82%E6%B0%91%E7%9B%A1%E9%87%8F%E5%8B%BF%E5%88%B0%E5%85%83%E6%9C%97/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E6%25B0%2591%25E5%25BB%25BA%25E8%2581%25AF%25E7%25B7%258A%25E6%2580%25A5%25E5%2591%25BC%25E7%25B1%25B2-%25E5%258D%2580%25E5%25A4%2596%25E5%25B8%2582%25E6%25B0%2591%25E7%259B%25A1%25E9%2587%258F%25E5%258B%25BF%25E5%2588%25B0%25E5%2585%2583%25E6%259C%2597%2F&d=P86Nric8SGsb572WK9RGd7ccVloK1XwbfTGMhSGe0oU%3D&h=a8e7e120\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E6%25B0%2591%25E5%25BB%25BA%25E8%2581%25AF%25E7%25B7%258A%25E6%2580%25A5%25E5%2591%25BC%25E7%25B1%25B2-%25E5%258D%2580%25E5%25A4%2596%25E5%25B8%2582%25E6%25B0%2591%25E7%259B%25A1%25E9%2587%258F%25E5%258B%25BF%25E5%2588%25B0%25E5%2585%2583%25E6%259C%2597%2F&h=90f8712a\" target=\"_blank\">https://thestandnews.com/politics/%E6%B0%91%E5%BB%BA%E8%81%AF%E7%B7%8A%E6%80%A5%E5%91%BC%E7%B1%B2-%E5%8D%80%E5%A4%96%E5%B8%82%E6%B0%91%E7%9B%A1%E9%87%8F%E5%8B%BF%E5%88%B0%E5%85%83%E6%9C%97/</a>"},{"pid":"996d74f993919398d9148b79a9ec6d3a727cc49c","tid":1370622,"uid":212626,"like":257,"dislike":2,"score":255,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T05:01:36.000Z","msg":"元朗變咗疫區<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"38f18c1b6601d0361fd02cace84be82b32992a0e","tid":1370622,"uid":23707,"like":284,"dislike":0,"score":284,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T05:01:56.000Z","msg":"希望民建聯永世撤出元朗，再撤出香港<br />\n擁抱大灣區"},{"pid":"b99667322397a120328fb48ac802215485e20018","tid":1370622,"uid":215611,"like":13,"dislike":3,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T05:02:02.000Z","msg":"民賤聯含撚啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n屌爆你老母個臭屎眼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4d126d67d47e15f3d9253ada2b6cef2c110732a2","tid":1370622,"uid":245644,"like":127,"dislike":0,"score":127,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T05:03:33.000Z","msg":"每星期申請一次，元朗會執幾多間商鋪？"},{"pid":"115470bbaa51f20ca46c3f3e19916ae13e38d3ab","tid":1370622,"uid":149361,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T05:04:37.000Z","msg":"關你撚事咩"},{"pid":"37f37caffd07563262962a26dc2c7c68025377bb","tid":1370622,"uid":6111,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T05:05:30.000Z","msg":"入去食野都犯法？<br />\n拉我囉戇鳩"},{"pid":"95dae373396f4e8121deeca85471d34a01aef3c5","tid":1370622,"uid":216789,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T05:05:56.000Z","msg":"<strong>慎防黑惡勢力蔓延禍港，提防本地非法操縱妓女賣淫集團</strong><br />\n<br />\n鑒於近日有無辜香港市民慘遭黑勢力人仕襲擊，現懇切呼籲各香港市民不論男女，